#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Armor Class** 20 (natural armor)    \n"
"**Hit Points** 210 (20d10 + 100)    \n"
"**Speed** 30 ft. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/iron_golem.md:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| STR     | DEX     | CON     | INT     | WIS     | CHA     |\n"
"|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|\n"
"| 24 (+7) | 9 (−1)  | 20 (+5) | 3 (−4)  | 11 (+0) | 1 (−5)  |\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/iron_golem.md:21
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Damage Immunities** fire, poison, psychic; bludgeoning, piercing, and "
"slashing from nonmagical attacks that aren't adamantine    \n"
"**Condition Immunities** charmed, exhaustion, frightened, paralyzed, "
"petrified, poisoned    \n"
"**Senses** darkvision 120 ft., passive Perception 10    \n"
"**Languages** understands the languages of its creator but can't speak    \n"
"**Challenge** 16 (15,000 XP) \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/iron_golem.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Fire Absorption.** Whenever the golem is subjected to fire damage, it "
"takes no damage and instead regains a number of hit points equal to the fire "
"damage dealt.    \n"
"**Immutable Form.** The golem is immune to any spell or effect that would "
"alter its form.    \n"
"**Magic Resistance.** The golem has advantage on saving throws against "
"spells and other magical effects.    \n"
"**Magic Weapons.** The golem's weapon attacks are magical. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/iron_golem.md:31
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions \n"
"**Multiattack.** The golem makes two melee attacks.    \n"
"**Slam.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +13 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ "
"20 (3d8 + 7) bludgeoning damage.    \n"
"**Sword.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +13 to hit, reach 10 ft., one "
"target. _Hit:_ 23 (3d10 + 7) slashing damage.    \n"
"**Poison Breath (Recharge 6).** The golem exhales poisonous gas in a 15-foot "
"cone. Each creature in that area must make a DC 19 Constitution saving "
"throw, taking 45 (10d8) poison damage on a failed save, or half as much "
"damage on a successful one.\n"
msgstr ""
